*******************************************************************************
ncomp (P)	the number of components to be used in discrete DOSY fitting
*******************************************************************************
NAME
	ncomp (P)

SYNOPSIS

DESCRIPTION 
	ncomp determines the number of components to be used in fitting
the signal decay in DOSY when the parameter dosyproc='discrete'.

OPTIONS
	ncomp should be an integer >0

FILES

SEE ALSO
	dosy

